## Tools & Technologies
- **Python Libraries**: Matplotlib, Seaborn, Plotly, Folium, GeoPandas
- **Business Intelligence**: Power BI, Tableau
- **Additional Tools**: Excel for data preparation

## Usage
Each visualization project includes:
- Source code or workbook files
- Documentation explaining the visualization choices
- Sample datasets or instructions to obtain them
- Requirements and dependencies

## Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/glendamakamadze/data-viz-portfolio.git
cd data-viz-portfolio

# Install required packages for Python examples
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

